=== Loi giai tu luan ===

Thong so: n = 6, k = 3, r = 3
g(x) = x^3 + x^2 + 1

STT  m(bin)      m(x)           c(bin)
------------------------------------------------------------
0    000         0              000000
1    001         x^2            110100
2    010         x              011010
3    011         x^2 + x        101110
4    100         1              001101
5    101         x^2 + 1        111001
6    110         x + 1          010111
7    111         x^2 + x + 1    100011

Ket qua: d_min = 3, phat hien 2 loi, sua 1 loi
